{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"d496888a-4a43-4a8a-81c1-8661f232c360","content":"No repo-specific MSTest plugins here, so here's the recommended setup based on current MSTest best practices:\n\n## 1. Project File (`MyTests.csproj`)\n\n```xml\n<Project Sdk=\"MSTest.Sdk/3.8\">\n\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n\n</Project>\n```\n\n`MSTest.Sdk` bundles the runner, framework, and analyzers — no extra `<PackageReference>` items needed.\n\n## 2. Enable Parallel Execution (`.runsettings`)\n\nCreate a `.runsettings` file at the project root:\n\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <Parallelize>\n      <Workers>0</Workers>          <!-- 0 = one worker per core -->\n      <Scope>ClassLevel</Scope>     <!-- classes run in parallel -->\n    </Parallelize>\n  </MSTest>\n</RunSettings>\n```\n\nThen reference it in your csproj (inside `<PropertyGroup>`):\n\n```xml\n<RunSettingsFilePath>$(MSBuildProjectDirectory)\\.runsettings</RunSettingsFilePath>\n```\n\n## 3. Make Database Tests Sequential\n\nUse `[DoNotParallelize]` on the class containing your database integration tests:\n\n```csharp\nusing Microsoft.VisualStudio.TestTools.UnitTesting;\n\n[TestClass]\n[DoNotParallelize]\npublic class DatabaseIntegrationTests\n{\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void Test_InsertRecord() { /* ... */ }\n\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void Test_ReadRecord() { /* ... */ }\n}\n```\n\n**Key points:**\n- **`[DoNotParallelize]`** on a class forces its tests to run sequentially *and* not concurrently with any parallel tests.\n- All other `[TestClass]` classes will run in parallel as configured.\n- `Scope=\"ClassLevel\"` means methods *within* a single class already run sequentially; parallelism is across classes. Use `MethodLevel` if you want even finer-grained parallelism.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"2e599381-5206-4a63-8794-007a78028901","outputTokens":533,"requestId":"604D:388A0A:25A6D3C:2846F25:6A03127D"},"id":"375e3a4d-9793-4b58-aab6-64e90da7f2b9","timestamp":"2026-05-12T11:44:08.457Z","parentId":"f1a39e4f-a10a-4575-bade-fdb36af677bf"}
